<tr valign="top">
<td class="grid">textarea
</td>
<td class="grid">Builds a <em>textarea</em> with the selected item attribute
value if used in Hash List context,
such as within an <span class="fixedwidth">[<a href="/icdocs/tags/item-list.html" title="item-list (tags)">item-list</a>]</span> tag.&nbsp;
<br><br>
the <em>textarea</em> will be built with 4 rows and 40 columns,
unless you specify a <span class="fixedwidth"><a href="#rows" title="&quot;rows&quot; heading on this page">rows</a></span> or <span class="fixedwidth"><a href="#cols" title="&quot;cols&quot; heading on this page">cols</a></span>
parameter.</td>
<td class="grid">All
</td>
