&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;3&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">3</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;4&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">4</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;5&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">5</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;10&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">10</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;15&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">15</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span> </span><span class="html_htmlParam def_Parameter">value</span><span class="html_htmlTagEqu def_Symbol">=</span><span class="html_htmlString def_String">&quot;20&quot;</span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><span class="html_htmlNumb def_Number">20</span><span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">option</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span></span><br>
<span class="html_htmlUnknowParam def_ParameterUnknown def_ParameterStrong def_Parameter"><span class="def_PairStart def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&lt;/</span></span><span class="html_htmlUnknowTag def_Tag"><span class="html_htmlOpenTag def_Keyword">select</span></span><span class="def_PairEnd def_Special"><span class="html_htmlTagBr def_OpenTag def_Tag">&gt;</span></span>
</span></span>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
<!-- end of code block -->
<p>
The above applies to any of the option building types:&nbsp;
<span class="fixedwidth">check</span>, <span class="fixedwidth">combo</span>, <span class="fixedwidth">combo_move</span>, <span class="fixedwidth">labels</span>,
<span class="fixedwidth">multiple</span>, <span class="fixedwidth">options</span>, <span class="fixedwidth">radio</span>,
<span class="fixedwidth">reverse_combo</span> and <span class="fixedwidth">select</span>.&nbsp;
It will refuse to produce more than 5000 options, by default,
but that limit can be changed using &quot;<span class="fixedwidth"><a href="/icdocs/config/Limit.html" title="Limit (config)">Limit</a> option_list <em>N</em></span>&quot; in the <em>local</em> (<span class="fixedwidth">catalog.cfg</span>) configuration,
where <em>N</em> is an integer greater than 0.
</p>
<a name="width"></a>
<h3>width</h3>
<p>
This is a quasi-alias for the <span class="fixedwidth"><a href="#cols" title="&quot;cols&quot; heading on this page">cols</a></span> parameter that only
works with the &quot;<span class="fixedwidth">text</span>&quot; and &quot;<span class="fixedwidth">password</span>&quot; widgets.&nbsp;
Use the &quot;<span class="fixedwidth"><a href="#cols" title="&quot;cols&quot; heading on this page">cols</a></span>&quot; parameter instead.
</p>
